r.d: A singly-linked list offers the ability to insert or delete nodes at any point within the list. A doubly-linked list also offers the ability to request previous nodes in the list.
r.n: Eliminate E_STRICT messages due to type-hinting. Enable tests installed by PEAR to actually be tested. Make several tests expected output work for both PHP 5.1.x and 5.2.x. Add more tests.
